<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.10">
<l>vaṇṭār poḻilcūḻ naṟaiyūrnampik keṉṟum</l>
<l>toṇṭāyk kaliya ṉōliceytamiḻ mālai</l>
<l>toṇṭī rivaipā ṭumiṉpāṭiniṉ ṟāṭa</l>
<l>vuṇṭē vicumpun tamakkillaitu yarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, sing these [verses] the Tamil garland composed by Kaliyaṉ</l>
<l>As service always to the noble of Naṟaiyūr, encircled by bee-filled gardens;</l>
<l>If [you] dance, continuing singing,</l>
<l>Heaven will be for you, and there will be no sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
